Compute the Hubble parameter $H(z)$ for a flat wCDM cosmology.

$$
H(z; H_0, \Omega_{{m,0}}, w_0) = \frac{{d_H(H_0)}}{{E(z; \Omega_{{m,0}}, w_0)}}
$$

