Compute the comoving distance using an analytic integral of the
Pade approximation.

$$
d_{{C}} = d_{{H}} \int_{{0}}^{{z}}
\frac{{dz'}}{{E(z'; \Omega_{{m,0}}, w_0)}}
$$

