Compute the absorption distance using an analytic integral of the
Pade approximation.

$$
d_{{A}} = \int_{{0}}^{{z}}
\frac{{dz' (1 + z')^2}}{{E(z'; \Omega_{{m,0}}, w_0)}}
$$

